Creating a release:
==================

Note: We are using the version number 0.30.9 simply as an example.

- Create a release distribution
./create-release.sh 0.30.9
Transfer ./genlop-0.30.9.tar.gz to dev.gentoo.org:/space/distfiles-local

- Clean up any extraneous files
git status
rm or mv any untracked files/directories

- Create a tag for the release
git tag genlop-0.30.9
git push origin genlop-0.30.9
